{"tid":793003,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SKE48退役偶像任職球場賣酒小妹  引粉絲圍觀拍照","createTime":"2018-08-25T04:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T06:07:20.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9a3bcc32690a4f86c374cccda4718dcf0e907b","tid":793003,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"日前，名古屋巨蛋球場舉辦棒球比賽，在球場內有人發現了前SKE48偶像中村優花，她退役後竟然擔任起球場的賣酒妹，還引起了眾多粉絲的圍觀拍照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/121531_77ea50965c3a0b7fd0a28f0f256f7d7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F121531_77ea50965c3a0b7fd0a28f0f256f7d7f.jpg&h=47c44830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2010年通過SKE48第4期生選拔合格，然後在團內活躍了將近一年左右的時間，後來因為學業因素宣布退團，於是在2011年底在表演完最後一場大型活動紅白後，正式的從SKE48畢業而且退出演藝圈到現在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/121548_75be975730c79e9f46eaa89f92e8ef94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F121548_75be975730c79e9f46eaa89f92e8ef94.jpg&h=8d285588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/121549_6f7812d8b6749d8efd5d6a76044a0f5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F121549_6f7812d8b6749d8efd5d6a76044a0f5c.jpg&h=f29b85d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/121601_2463c95a387b781f89f6d59fa9d2f519.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F121601_2463c95a387b781f89f6d59fa9d2f519.jpg&h=e8d8abaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/121700_717e3a708cdded317aff3c43e001aa4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F121700_717e3a708cdded317aff3c43e001aa4b.jpg&h=4815af32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/121700_035b5628c8a314cf45e6a7f993013e11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F121700_035b5628c8a314cf45e6a7f993013e11.jpg&h=2af72f2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/121701_88f17b4bb4eecdeaca57aff7c11b94d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F121701_88f17b4bb4eecdeaca57aff7c11b94d5.jpg&h=305d9285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/121701_aa2ddc248ccb094e99b704299e1fbf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F121701_aa2ddc248ccb094e99b704299e1fbf68.jpg&h=59e38992&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7052511b94a11dbf5f40f830a82409fd3b394c6b","tid":793003,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"有無人仲記得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28dbcd2868932dce0b1518214a961570e3715db2","tid":793003,"uid":29496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"幾靚"},{"pid":"8c931f01e4f010992c2f779302cc04b38077b2cd","tid":793003,"uid":8435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"賣啤酒可能仲好搵過留喺SKE48"}]}